    "description": {
      "value": "<p>An empty, slimy invertebrate shell, it glows dimly.</p><p>As an action or bonus action, you coat your trick weapon with energy for 5 rounds.</p><p>For the duration your weapon emits a 10-foot radius of dim light, and, once per turn, when you would cause a creature to make a concentration check as the result of you hitting them with your Trick Weapon, they subtract your Bold Counter bonus from their next concentration check.</p><p>If this causes the creature to lose concentration, you gain temporary chakra equal to the cost of the jutsu.</p>",
